00:07:22.310 --> 00:07:25.810
others are known for their meat, or even for their milk,

00:07:25.810 --> 00:07:31.310
and sheep have different temperaments, some are more docile than others.

00:07:31.310 --> 00:07:36.310
But not one type of sheep has all of the desirable characteristics.

00:07:36.310 --> 00:07:39.310
What a fitting illustration that Jesus used.

00:07:39.310 --> 00:07:43.310
This one united flock of precious sheep comes from where?

00:07:43.310 --> 00:07:49.310
It comes from over 230 different lands around the earth, out of all nations, tribes, peoples and tongues.

00:07:49.310 --> 00:07:55.310
We all have strength, we all have weaknesses, so it takes work to remain united.

00:07:55.310 --> 00:08:02.310
And what is the key? What did we discuss? Education? Application.

00:08:02.310 --> 00:08:07.310
And what did Jesus say? The sheep would do his other sheep.

00:08:07.310 --> 00:08:12.310
All of those that are together, they will listen to my voice.

00:08:12.310 --> 00:08:17.310
All of Jesus' sheep, the little flock and the other sheep alike, work hard to apply his teachings.

00:08:17.310 --> 00:08:21.310
Consider just a few from Jesus' sermon on the Mount.

00:08:21.310 --> 00:08:27.310
We try hard to make peace with our brother if we've offended him in some way.

00:08:27.310 --> 00:08:30.310
We try our best to love our enemies.

00:08:30.310 --> 00:08:33.309
We forgive others, their trespasses.

00:08:33.309 --> 00:08:39.309
We do our best to stop judging others who for their actions or for their motives.

00:08:39.309 --> 00:08:44.309
And fundamentally, we treat others as we would like them to treat us.

00:08:44.309 --> 00:08:49.309
Because of our rich diet of spiritual food, we produce peaceful qualities, peaceful fruit.

00:08:49.309 --> 00:08:53.309
Education and application leads to peace.

00:08:54.309 --> 00:08:57.309
With what result? What did Jesus say?

00:08:57.309 --> 00:09:00.309
We become one flock, one shepherd.

00:09:00.309 --> 00:09:02.309
We enjoy precious unity as a group.

00:09:02.309 --> 00:09:08.309
But what about us as individuals in our work environment or in our daily activities?

00:09:08.309 --> 00:09:09.309
What's our responsibility?

00:09:09.309 --> 00:09:16.309
No, please, how the Apostle Paul highlighted the qualities that we continually need to cultivate.

00:09:16.309 --> 00:09:18.309
Ephesians chapter four.

