00:10:24.309 --> 00:10:27.309
These contribute to the uniting bond of peace.

00:10:27.309 --> 00:10:29.309
It takes earnest effort.

00:10:29.309 --> 00:10:31.309
We earnestly need to apply ourselves.

00:10:31.309 --> 00:10:34.309
But Jehovah blesses our efforts to display such qualities.

00:10:34.309 --> 00:10:37.309
So what have we considered this morning?

00:10:37.309 --> 00:10:43.309
Although the world continues to become more and more divided, Jehovah's people become more and more united.

00:10:43.309 --> 00:10:45.309
Jehovah unifies his people.

00:10:45.309 --> 00:10:48.309
